data.description: This beautiful home, carefully taken care of and renovated over time, will get your attention at first sight. Three bedrooms, one of which is converted into an office but can still be a bedroom, and a sun room with access directly to the backyard. The two-car garage has access to the shelter, and the backyard has a roomy shed for your extras. Truly, what more could you want? Don't miss out on this amazing home. P.S. The backyard previously had a pool, and the seller removed it but has treated the yard on its way back to full growth.
